# Build-context hygiene for the frontend image (deploy/Dockerfile.frontend).
# Build context is THIS directory: `docker build -f deploy/Dockerfile.frontend
# -t sec-gs-frontend:local frontend`. Two goals: keep the context small, and —
# critically — keep secrets and local build state OUT of every image layer.
# Mirrors frontend/.gitignore + the repo-root .gitignore env rules.

# --- Secrets & local env files (NEVER bake into an image layer) -----------
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.cer
*.p12
*.pfx
*.token

# --- Installed deps + build output (re-created inside the image) ----------
# node_modules is re-installed with --frozen-lockfile; a prior local .next
# build (and its standalone tree) must never leak host state into the image.
node_modules/
.pnp/
.pnp.*
.next/
out/

# --- Test + coverage artefacts (not needed to build the standalone bundle) -
coverage/
tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
*.log
tests/
vitest.config.ts

# --- VCS, editor, OS --------------------------------------------------------
.git/
.gitignore
.dockerignore
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
